<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Informational message: WorkSpaces Launch Errors>
We are investigating increased errors when launching new WorkSpaces in the EU-WEST-1 Region.

<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Service is operating normally: [RESOLVED] WorkSpaces Launch Errors>
Between September 11 6:35 PM and September 12 2:24 AM PDT we experienced increased errors when launching new WorkSpaces in the EU-WEST-1 Region. The issue has been resolved and the service is operating normally.
